    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This unit has had the critical dual-VANOS system serviced and the rear subframe mounting points professionally reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary structural concerns. The engine pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from individual throttle bodies and a recently flushed cooling system. It retains its factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential and staggered Style 67 wheels. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and the interior displays light bolster wear indicative of its 'good' driver status, the drivetrain is exceptionally tight with no signs of rod bearing fatigue or fluid seepage. A visceral, analog performance machine for the discerning driver.",
